[For information on the low pathogenicity avian influenza (LPAI) situation in South Africa, please refer to comments by Mod.AS in the ProMED-mail post, archive number 20140626.2567831.

In addition, a new outbreak of LPAI H7N7 was reported in ostriches. This outbreak is associated with the event which started on 31 Jan 2014. See follow-up report No. 1 (http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/temp/reports/en_fup_0000015852_20140819_184125.pdf). - Mod.CRD

